'''夜曲Op. 55'''是[[弗雷德里克·肖邦|蕭邦]]的一組[[夜曲|夜曲]]作品，於1842-1844年創作，1844年8月出版<ref name="amg">{{Cite web|title=Nocturnes (2) for piano, Op. 55, ... {{!}} Details|url=https://www.allmusic.com/composition/nocturnes-2-for-piano-op-55-ct-122-123-mc0002393162|access-date=2021-10-14|work=AllMusic|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211030054729/https://www.allmusic.com/composition/nocturnes-2-for-piano-op-55-ct-122-123-mc0002393162}}</ref>。這兩首作品獻給他的學生{{link-en|简·斯特灵|Jane Stirling}}<ref name="gutenberg1">{{Cite web |url=http://www.gutenberg.org/dirs/etext04/fkchc10.txt |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-05-22 |archive-date=2009-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090926110055/http://www.gutenberg.org/dirs/etext04/fkchc10.txt |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

